
 Copy file easybeans.xml to be avaible in tomcat classloader for this
application for this application

 For example, if tomcat root is /opt/tomcat, than place this file in
  /opt/tomcat/webapps/ow2-easybeans-hibernate-1.0.0/WEB-INF/classes

 also, does not forgott place jdbc drivers in tomcat libs

 for details see http://www.easybeans.org/doc/userguide/en/integrated/userguide.html#id331028

 Original file (without out changes) live in 
 ow2-easybeans-src-1.0.0/modules/core/src/main/java/org/ow2/easybeans/server/easybeans-default.xml

